{"tid":1466138,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［Game Theory][博奕論］攬炒的重要","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T03:55:34.000Z","uid":48516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"78b7907547fa551cbf553ea8341fd0687daff610","tid":1466138,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"Game theory 有個著名的模型叫 chicken game 懦夫博奕。模型中，兩名車手相對驅車而行，誰最先轉彎的一方被恥笑為「膽小鬼」（chicken），讓另一方勝出，因此這博弈模型在英文中稱為The Game of Chicken（懦夫遊戲），但如果兩人拒絕轉彎，任由兩車相撞，最終誰都無法受益。這套模型在政治、經濟上經常使用，也被用來形容相互保證毀滅的核戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n正常情況結果如下（A得益，B得益）：<br />\n                A 轉彎        A加速<br />\nB轉彎  （3，3）   （10，-3）<br />\nB加速  （-3，10）（-10，-10）<br />\n<br />\n在相撞前，只有其中一方轉彎才會分出勝負。但這樣無法保證誰勝誰負。但係！有一個必勝法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。就係一開始就丟咗個肽盤！<br />\n<br />\n結果變為<br />\n<br />\n               A加速          A加速<br />\nB轉彎 （10, -3）   （10,-3）<br />\nB加速 （-10,-10）（-10,-10）<br />\n<br />\n由於 A只會加速，B只可以在 -10 與 -3  之間選擇。理性的 player 一定會轉彎。咁樣我地就可以成功了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，喺現實世界點丟咗個肽盤係一個問題，可以係機場，可以係交易所<br />\n<br />\n所以，就算唔想攬炒，都要有攬炒嘅心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c9bc43a44ffa7a040ad8267ce7a9fe2b1e2ece","tid":1466138,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"32aebe639fbd6d340cd6d4e8094db50a450ba6ce","tid":1466138,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3d04879779070b2b5eb748bf14e18a281df54f","tid":1466138,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:55:34.000Z","msg":"其實只要將-10降低到細過-3 <br />\n或者將-3推高到大過-10<br />\n就可以實現到必勝法。<br />\n<br />\n現實中就等於降低大家認為攬炒既嚴重性，<br />\n或者提高大家認為唔攬炒既嚴重性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}